{"tid":834143,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"隔夜息抽升至接近4厘","createTime":"2018-09-24T04:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T11:35:44.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5c0bf161dcb9b05b593b09f3b54a3add2860f067","tid":834143,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f578e0f592c77cd2820f73c29276218533eeb89","tid":834143,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"港匯今(24日)先升後回跌，高低位7.7980/7.8132，現貨美電新報7.8114。<br />\n<br />\n美聯儲本周將舉行議息會議，市場料加息四分之一厘。港元拆息全線上升，隔夜拆息連升三日，今急升至約3.85厘，創2007年10月後近十一年高位，並高於一周、一個月甚至更長時間拆息呈「倒掛」；一周拆息連升五日至約3.26厘，創2008年9月金融海嘯開始後約十年高位；另與供樓利率相關的一個月拆息亦連升五日，今升幅近28點子，據外電統計指是創下2008年12月以來最大升幅，至約2.169厘近十年高位。"},{"pid":"69b75bbb437f4ea825fc769abfbf2fedd012a91a","tid":834143,"uid":186594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:48:26.000Z","msg":"升得幾日<br />\n唔計"},{"pid":"04852b446b53b76ea90758906107ffa4e861c4f7","tid":834143,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"銀行唔加 唔計"},{"pid":"72fb8d7df106098e51e6886a17acfcea958ce353","tid":834143,"uid":89225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"就假期。唔計"},{"pid":"5047a8b1260da033a69bd0b29481d91613934354","tid":834143,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"銀行同業加唔計"},{"pid":"902f7bd393edf01ba9dcc717d3712274dd370420","tid":834143,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4a567b4004a8f83614382cce9fc7a005abf49f7","tid":834143,"uid":39326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f578e0f592c77cd2820f73c29276218533eeb89","tid":834143,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:09:41.000Z","ms